title: We need a logo for our startup!
description:
Our startup works is developing and manufacturing machinery for the pharmaceutical industry. We are targeting the field of quality control, lab digitalization and robotization.
We are developing machines which are using inkjet printing to print on various surfaces. That is the reason for the word JET in our name. The logo should incorporate some sort of visual element which is attributed to ink jetting (dot, drop, stream,..) and our brand name.
other_notes: I’m open to ideas on the type of logo that’s best for my brand.
